 VTuber碓冰Kuria被任命为内阁府“第6届空间开发利用奖”公关人物https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usui-clear-became-a-pr-character-for-the-6th-space-development-and-utilization-awards-by-cabinet-office-of-japan/ https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usui-clear-became-a-pr-character-for-the-6th-space-development-and-utilization-awards-by-cabinet-office-of-japan/#respondp2y_admin Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:59:49 +0000 VTuberバーチャル宇宙科学TwitterYouTubeYouTuberバーチャルYouTuber個人勢内閣府宇宙開発宇推くりあ日本政府高市早苗 https://p2y.jp/?p=103282 <p>在2023年10月13日（令和5年）的新闻发布会上，内阁府特务大臣高市早苗介绍了内阁主办的“第六届宇宙开发利用奖”的公关性质办公室，VTuber Kuria Usu（独立）。据宣布，先生 [...]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usui-clear-became-a-pr-character-for-the-6th-space-development-and-utilization-awards-by-cabinet-office-of-japan/">被任命为内阁府“第六届空间开发利用奖”公关人物的 VTuber 臼井久利亚 (Kuria Usui)</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>在2023年10月13日（令和5年）的新闻发布会上，内阁府特务大臣高市早苗介绍了“<strong>第六届宇宙开发利用奖”</strong>公关人物VTuber <strong>Usu Kuria</strong> （独立） 》由内阁府主办，宣布他已被任命。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" width="1184" height="666" data-attachment-id="103292" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-usui-clear-became-a-pr-character-for-the-6th-space-development-and-utilization-awards-by-cabinet-office-of-japan/vtuber_usui_clear_became_a_pr_character_for_the_6th_space_development_and_utilization_awards_by_cabinet_office_of_japan/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/vtuber_usui_clear_became_a_pr_character_for_the_6th_space_development_and_utilization_awards_by_cabinet_office_of_japan.jpg" data-orig-size="1184,666" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quo